<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Advanced standing may be earned through the Advanced Placement Program of the College Board for a total of 32 credits for those examinations that correspond to courses in the Guilford curriculum.  Placement requires Advanced Placement scores of three or better; credit requires Advanced Placement scores of four or better.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.guilford.edu/admission/traditional-degree-programs/requirements/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

